        %h4.modal-title How can we help you?
      .modal-body
        %h5 Welcome to fablabs.io!
        %p
          Here are few suggestions about how we can help you and how you can participate
          and talk with us if you have any question or problem regarding the Fablabs.io
          platform.
        %hr/
        %h5 Discuss with the community
        %p
          You can ask for support to the administrators and the whole community
          in the Fablabs.io Discuss section within the
          = succeed "." do
            %a{:href => "https://discuss.fablabs.io/c/site-feedback"} Site feedback category
          %a{:href => "https://discuss.fablabs.io/c/site-feedback"} Site feedback category
          we would also love to hear your ideas and suggestions regarding Fablabs.io,
          its features, development, how it works and how we can improve it.
        %a.button{:href => "https://discuss.fablabs.io/c/site-feedback"} Discuss with the community
        %hr/


        %h5 Help with the technical development on GitHub
        %p
          If you have instead messages regarding the technical development or bugs
          of the platform, we would ask you to discuss these on the Fablabs.io repositories
          on GitHub (Fablabs.io is free/open source software!) at
          = succeed "." do
            %a{:href => "https://github.com/fablabbcn/fablabs"} https://github.com/fablabbcn/fablabs
        %a.button{:href => "https://github.com/fablabbcn/fablabs"} Join the development
        %hr/
        %h5 E-mail the administrators
        %p
          If you need instead to contact the administrators of Fablabs.io, please
          write to
          = succeed "." do
            %a{:href => "mailto:webmasters@fablabs.io"} webmasters@fablabs.io
        %a.button{:href => "mailto:webmasters@fablabs.io"} Write an e-mail to the administrators

